Item Tracking System
By DeepSeek

PYTHON INSTALL (WINDOWS):
1. Download Python 3 from python.org/downloads
2. Run installer
3. CHECK "Add Python to PATH" (important!)
4. Click "Install Now"
5. Verify in Command Prompt:
   python --version

USAGE:
1. Place scanner.py in your preferred folder
2. Open Command Prompt (Win+R, type cmd)
3. Navigate to folder:
   cd path\to\folder
4. Run:
   python scanner.py

KEY COMMANDS:
1 - Check IN items
2 - Check OUT items
3 - Move items
4 - Register locations
7 - Create batches
Type 'finish' to exit scanning mode

DATA:
- Local SQLite database: item_tracking.db
- Barcode format: XXXX_DD_MM_YY_GX (batch)
                  XXXX_DD_MM_YY_GX_XXXX (item)
